5. An endoscope, comprising:
an insertion unit having one end portion inserted into a body;
an operation unit that is coupled to the other end of the insertion unit, and operates the one end of the insertion unit to perform flexural movement by using an operation module;
a joint unit connected to one end of the operation unit; and
the opening and closing unit of claim 1 which is disposed on the operation unit and selectively communicates the insertion unit and the joint unit.
